{"tid":2434993,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇完鍾培生林作記者會之後又重溫多次《破壞之王》？","createTime":"2021-03-06T02:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T03:47:28.000Z","uid":18584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"80d54ac8b62c04bb48d8f1e72128f8e88de4e334","tid":2434993,"uid":18584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc8159e5f73b56549fe4a2a11454571607a651c","tid":2434993,"uid":176944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"周星馳響戲入面係一個外賣仔，叫何金銀，鍾意咗黑熊條女阿麗，但唔夠黑熊打。周星馳於是搵咗拳手鬼仔達學武，點知鬼仔達只係呃何金銀錢，亂教一通，但何金銀竟然練得出武功，打贏咗黑熊。<br />\n<br />\n無耐斷水流大師兄搶走咗阿麗，鬼仔達帶何金銀發出挑戰書。擂台上，鬼仔達運用心理戰控制賽情，就咁樣何金銀輕易贏出。點知斷水流大師兄終於使出真功夫，何金銀利用幸運輪向斷水流使出無敵風火輪&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"613fcefe95ef6daf9202d17163a08fec5bec2d27","tid":2434993,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba54577fb97d244768382a4b8be4df249637b16c","tid":2434993,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"原來保險佬仲有個花名係咩銀嘅"},{"pid":"30b9c761b35fd2a8f6f90912281c7d4b9b75a8ed","tid":2434993,"uid":49415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80d54ac8b62c04bb48d8f1e72128f8e88de4e334","tid":2434993,"uid":18584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2435010\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2435010</a>"},{"pid":"75788de2ca93ab985c47fc3